---
title: Roasted Cauliflower & Chicken Bengali Biryani with Currants & Yoghurt
description: Curry on rice is all well and good, but when the rice itself is cooked with the curry paste? Now that’s magical. Studded with sweet
currants and roasted cauliflower and chicken, this dish packs flavour in every bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
